    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divinastros 是一款 roguelike 牌组构建游戏，专注于用您的牌获得高分！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/04e4fba67bc24944356a6f44e4126730.poster.avif?t=1772306756\" width=600 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/04e4fba67bc24944356a6f44e4126730.webm?t=1772306756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/04e4fba67bc24944356a6f44e4126730.mp4?t=1772306756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择您的牌，并与塔罗牌和十二宫进行组合，以获得最佳构建！与希腊野兽和众神战斗，结识不同的角色，发现新的塔罗牌组，并前往奥林匹斯山。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/5e5294461f09f7d69985c475fcdb56df.poster.avif?t=1772306756\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/5e5294461f09f7d69985c475fcdb56df.webm?t=1772306756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/5e5294461f09f7d69985c475fcdb56df.mp4?t=1772306756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次运行都是独一无二的！根据不同的十二宫星座调整您的游戏玩法，击败试图阻止您的众多 Boss。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/4ab4046c7fecbc654599923f4532b228.poster.avif?t=1772306756\" width=598 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/4ab4046c7fecbc654599923f4532b228.webm?t=1772306756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/4ab4046c7fecbc654599923f4532b228.mp4?t=1772306756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识各种友好的神话生物和人物。他们每个人都会为您提供帮助和新的任务来完成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/5aa6b8bb4e52850ce5c74d822e4592ad.poster.avif?t=1772306756\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/5aa6b8bb4e52850ce5c74d822e4592ad.webm?t=1772306756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033030/extras/5aa6b8bb4e52850ce5c74d822e4592ad.mp4?t=1772306756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 88 张独特的大阿卡那塔罗牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 12 个星座，每个都有其独特的游戏玩法</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 8 个召唤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 4 个不同的塔罗牌组</p>",
